{"title":"交谈","authors":["唐恒"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"交谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要下井了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的朋友，此刻已近正午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间要把你扔到很远的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去种植阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从地面步行到地层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的脚步响了整整十年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年后日子会渐渐好起来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你眼中热辣辣的欲望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会切削着煤的积郁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我因此感到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我读过的一本寓言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的矿灯像崭新锃亮的钢轨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静地延伸在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巷道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥汗如雨的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拒绝感冒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背着风的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你潇洒地挥一挥手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后面有你初次下矿的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可以陪他们说些话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说点他们不知道的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可以朗诵炉中煤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起流泪的红烛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为生命中有一段挖煤的岁月喝彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果疲惫了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就靠着坑木打个盹吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然这样老去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也相信这里面有你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春岁月和职业良心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}